**** Freewrite
- "What about this class excites you most?"

It was very pleasing to hear that grades will be argued for. This is
something that sounds very confortable to me. Having a smaller class
size is also interesting, as it seems it may allow for more involved
discussions or arguments.

- "What about this class scares you most?"

English courses in general tend to scare me a tad, in that the learning outcomes for 
some previously taken did not seem to explicitly stated -- unecessary ambiguity. 
**** Why We Make Arguments
I like this idea of argumentation, as a non-negative activity. 
- Ethos
- Pathos
- Logos
- Kairos
- Deliberative (Future)
- Epideictic (Present)
- Forensic (Past)
